==English==
===Phrasal verb===
'''to make ends meet'''
#{{idiom}} to have [[enough]] [[money]] to cover [[expenses]]; to [[get by]] financially; to get through the pay period (sufficient to meet the next payday). 
#:''It is hard for someone to '''make ends meet''' these days on a single income.''

